## ‚öôÔ∏è Configuration

### Backend - Variables d'Environnement

| Variable | Description | D√©faut |
|----------|-------------|--------|
| `PORT` | Port du serveur | 3000 |
| `NODE_ENV` | Environnement | development |
| `REDIS_URL` | URL Redis | redis://localhost:6379 |
| `TOMTOM_API_KEY` | Cl√© API TomTom | - |
| `ALLOWED_ORIGINS` | CORS origins | http://localhost:3001 |

### Configuration Redis Cache

```javascript
// backend/src/config/cache.js
const cacheTTL = {
  traffic: 300,      // 5 minutes
  routes: 600,       // 10 minutes
  geocoding: 3600    // 1 heure
};
```

### Algorithme Multi-Crit√®res

```javascript
// Pond√©ration des crit√®res (total = 1.0)
const weights = {
  duration: 0.35,     // Dur√©e prioritaire
  transfers: 0.25,    // Nombre de correspondances
  walking: 0.15,      // Distance de marche
  congestion: 0.15,   // Congestion trafic
  density: 0.10       // Densit√© urbaine
};
```

